Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mom and my sisters moved \Noverseas because of Dad's job...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so now I'm living alone \Nstarting this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my first time living \Nalone only lasted for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rikka. I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already. School starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a virtual repeat of \Nlast year's attempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to keep my dark chunibyo \Nhistory safely hidden away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and start life anew in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rikka Takanashi here foiled me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I command you to awaken, \NRikka Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, Wicked Lord Shingan. \NThe time of awakening has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, is sunny side up okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark side up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunny side up" it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave her too many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the ribbon \Nfor my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp! Was it their doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to \Nget it ready yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for goofing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll yank out your antenna hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't! It's my \Nmost attractive feature!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka's mother also had to move out \Nof town for work this spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which led to Rikka having to \Nlive on her own as well, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are your things being moved out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they finally made their move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Rikka's grandfather accidentally \Nlet go of their apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'll have to live with me \Nuntil your new place is sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating emergency code: Triple Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Rikka temporarily \Ncame to live with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pleasant to be woken up by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would never fly with the priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied to Toka and told her I'd \Nplaced Rikka in a small apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we are one week into \Nour deceitful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera, I give you my demonic fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am positive you are \Nimmune to red fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This proves nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try one. They taste as \Ngood as strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming more and \Nmore like the priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you under her influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fluid! The green, squishy \Nmatter is attacking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stay perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wiping at it will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to dab at it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:44.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're heading out, please do take \Na collapsible umbrella with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say we're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a couple, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you get to romance from \Nthis kind of a starting point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even had a normal \Ngirlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so having a first girlfriend with \Nchunibyo sets the bar even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things settled down in a way that \Nisn't much different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guten morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shinka Nibutani, and I'm in \NYear Two in high school starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school two syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to say this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what you promised yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the hieroglyphs, the \Nhateful magic barrier attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,triggered by the Freemasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our uninvited guests the \Nunfathomable parallel world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean our discussion about \Nperforming the Schrodinger's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cat experiment using Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know. How we're living \Ntogether at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. That.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only thing \NI spoke to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should drop by the \Nrealty office again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are referring to my new \Nbase, it has already been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the demon world of \Nthe impossibly Wicked One,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,invisible to mere mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll yank out your antenna hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you lovebirds are already at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Isshiki. Makoto Isshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! The guy in \Nthe Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who sacrificed everything \Nfor upperclassman Kumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the crew cut guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Crew Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that! That \Nversion of me is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at my Rock'n'Roll hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki, what happened to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go visit the student councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting it all wrong, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair type changed when it grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kumin! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka and Togashi. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both new Second Years today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're a Third Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. And it's such a let-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you'll have to \Nstudy for university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh, that isn't what I \Nmean. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Year Three is sooo next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it told me to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how Morisummer always \Nmakes everybody laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growing older brings many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning! What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am wearing regulation attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How do you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you experiencing advanced senility?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, if I might have a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.99,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DEKO                                                                                                      \NDEKO MIDDLE                                                                                               MIDDLE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, let's all share \Nanother lively school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you for that speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a lot of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that's all going \Nto change this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I will claw my way \Nto the top of this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The next speech comes \Nfrom our new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}...represented by Sanae Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I am the new student \Nrepresentative, Sanae Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}With the warm days of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}...the trees become enrobed \Nin fresh, new green livery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that she got better grades \Nthan you had last year, Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Our student lives also begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe everyone knows \Nthat in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are white \Nworlds and dark worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Seeing spirits requires \Nthe proper heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Love is everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, Nibutani has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We share the same class \Nonce again, Light Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ever are you saying, Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nanase is our home room teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told to get my hair \Ncut for school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know? It's \Nyour own damned fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are we in the same class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm in Class 3 next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that relief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made no attempt to hide your relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this beautiful girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Togashi's friend? My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Pot, meet kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only bringing this up \Nbecause we share a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have clearly instructed \NTakanashi not to share...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our middle school \Nmemories with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pondered all summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pondered my decision to attend \Nthis particular high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really intend to spend three \Nyears of my life in that loser's club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant to Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,User of the Mjolnir \NHammer, Sanae Dekomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is hereby reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the deviously \Ndevious Fake Morisummer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would dare stage an attack \Non me in my temporary guise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now observe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spin right left, and left right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing revolutions shall produce \Na kink between dimensions and space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by adding an additional revolution, \NI shall produce unlimited power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! The Mjolnir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have weak semicircular canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori will not be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Rich Cheese (6 pcs)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're such an \Nenergetic First Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a reward, I will \Ngive you the cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love. So. Much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One must deal with trouble \Nof one's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paging a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to the staff \Nroom immediately. I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please report to the \Nstaff room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school has been \Noverrun by terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing. The school mailed \Nat least three to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all came back returned to sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be due to the fact that my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,existence had been \Nerased from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we phone you, it says \Nthat number is not in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My existence had been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you exist right now, so \Nperhaps it'll go through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eye! My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Far-East Magical Napping \NSociety - Summer Thereof
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed to buy it, but we \Ncan't keep this up forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just try to take a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here and join us, Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incubus lives in that coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even one forged in the darkness \Nsuch as I dare not approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once experienced a frightening \Ndream while under its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What did you dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, the light! The Light \NBeing is paralyzing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is "ow" in the form of a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had to choose, where \Nwould you want to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we were talking about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding your new base \Nand battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The base where my Wicked Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingan and the Dark \NFlame Master manifest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is also an excellent \Ngeomagnetic focal point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it that's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that idiot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what she did to my \Ncostume for Theatre Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PERMANENT MARKER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must search for a new base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea where you \Nshould set up house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I favor a subterranean labyrinth, \Nbut a medieval castle will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Past the corner store, there's a castle \Nbuilding that says "Parliament" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Stay away from that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I didn't realize \Nhow expensive rent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I knew it might be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't know \Nmuch about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be barred from this place once \NI have transferred to my new base?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't come here when I \Ncommute to and from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to go to your room to \Nreport activity in the magical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drop by to pick you up for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find you a place \Nnearby so I can visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi's apartment is \Nvacant. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you move, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We leave for Italy soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you won't give me your new \Naddress or answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You are attempting \Nto maintain secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to tail Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, your loyal servant, will \Nbuy you the time you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masters, please evacuate to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize who you're up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the priestess who, \Nin a previous batle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once force-fed me a \Nmass of rotten dairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wish for a worthier opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Your hand! Your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUMMY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your intent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're wrong! This \Nisn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fake Morisummer's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It your fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deeply respect you, Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my master's sister, \NI am at your command!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to throw me under the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, prepare for combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assume positions and \Nprepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She easily deflected \Nyour Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! O!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! O! V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! O! V! E!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a physical attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,(DEMON GOD GUN) MA SHIN GAN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrostire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's arrostire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "oven roasted."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shacked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're living together as \Nboyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please control your \Ndisgusting imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're the one \Nwith the dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what? I, Dekomori, am \Nalways pure of thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone beet red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a little kid, you \Nhave a really dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! Be quiet, \Nyou big-boobed freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shacking is sooo shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's really \Nnot what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that a full grown \Nboy like yourself had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,....but to shack up with \Nmy little sister with whom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dissolved your pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who dumped whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! I'm saying we \Nare not "shacking up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's mostly because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,concerned about leaving \NRikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost a week now, and \Nnothing of the sort is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of what sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our contract remains unaltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we're \Nnot "living together"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's it! We're roommates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a home share situation. You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that logic will fly by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I will permit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, you \Ncannot live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will find her an apartment. If \Nyou have a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will take Rikka to Italy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical society! The Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I to be imprisoned in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Italy is home to the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vatican, Sixth Sense, \NI see dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home to the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you were told I was coming \Nback for the new school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka has been living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she doesn't have \Nher own place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of rooms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was also concerned \Nabout leaving Rikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would act as supervisor, \Nit should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please let her stay \Nhere just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and find your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, my life alone with \NRikka came to an abrupt end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TOGASHI MAIL FOR NAKANISHI HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and three teenagers began \Nlife together in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta's notebook. I forgot \Nto return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone new move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never was able to \Nget her apartment back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

